{"tid":836351,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【加息前賣樓】3字頭陳生500萬full pay買LP6：有閒錢就買","createTime":"2018-09-25T14:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T16:18:32.000Z","uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f0e813cf1a8624874fa1fa725c8a64493a5cec","tid":836351,"uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:43:17.000Z","msg":"【加息前賣樓】3字頭陳生500萬full pay買LP6：有閒錢就買<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180925/small/1537853069_a126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180925%2Fsmall%2F1537853069_a126.jpg&h=ebbdcefe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日出康城LP6開售707伙，吸引不少年輕買家入市。80後陳先生從事金融業，是次斥資「五球」買入LP6 1房單位作投資用，更表示「full pay 」入市，他指：「有閒錢咪買囉！」對於加息，他表示唔擔心，相信樓市會穩定發展。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180925&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58721143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180925%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58721143&d=7iDsfgrlGht%2Fgv6gDAikRf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=54dfde90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180925%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58721143&h=cc0f6c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180925&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58721143</a>"},{"pid":"3f9fbb3443c3aafbc8738382a75173d57c2356cf","tid":836351,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"full pay <br />\n<br />\n太多有實力既人<br />\n<br />\n撚會跌"},{"pid":"2ad8290a13334a11e08249fb52621d65fc0f7e8a","tid":836351,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:48:41.000Z","msg":"500萬閒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f4e6fc4d82c8eb193b352d8eb9ee9c71a33ae0","tid":836351,"uid":4258,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201